Do not approach. This area is
under military investigation.

rows.label: qst006102_msg0002
rows.name:
This stone is still under investigation.
We cannot have civilians touching
it and possibly breaking it.

rows.label: qst006102_msg0101
rows.name:
Oh, you are a member of the
royal family! You would not
handle the stone roughly.

rows.label: qst006102_msg0102
rows.name:
Please, investigate to
your heart's content.
